This is a technical preview of what will be the upcoming version of Nitrocid 0.2.1. Many features, which may make it to the final release, are missing.

We can't provide an exact ETA for the final release, but contributions, feedback, and suggestions are welcome.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added FreeBSD support
- `[*]` Refactored thread management code
- `[*]` Made the Windows installer more modular
- `[*]` Updated Terminaux to v8.5
- `[*]` Updated SQL and Cryptography's XML libraries to fix security issues
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://github.com/Aptivi/Nitrocid/issues/new).

